metadata.creator: Dave Trautman
metadata.description: This episode focusses on the Chilean community in Edmonton, there were three guests on the show talking about the current issues in Chile, such as the government, politics and religion. Also features traditional Chilean dances from different regions in Chile.
metadata.title: Programa Nosotros. La comunidad de Chile en Edmonton
